msgid ""
"I2P+ requires a web browser configured to use the resident HTTP proxy in "
"order to browse websites on the I2P network."
msgstr ""
"يتطلب I2P متصفح ويب تم تكوينه لاستخدام وكيل HTTP المقيم لتصفح مواقع الويب "
"على شبكة I2P."

#: /tmp/build-i2p/apps/routerconsole/java/build/../../jsp/WEB-INF/classes/net/i2p/router/web/jsp/wizard_jsp.java:706
